id: "class:fighter#buckler_duelist"
name: "Buckler Duelist"
description: "These duelists use their bucklers both to defend themselves and to launch\
  \ unexpected strikes while chopping and hewing at their foes' unprotected bodies\
  \ and heads with their falcatas. They wear any type of armor, but favor bucklers,\
  \ and are comfortable using both hands for offense and defense."
