  label: null
  type: null
  description: "At 5th level, a buckler duelist gains a +1 bonus on attack and damage\
    \ rolls when wielding a falcata and buckler that applies to attacks made by either\
    \ hand. These bonuses increase by +1 for every four levels beyond 5th. With a\
    \ full-attack action, a buckler duelist may alternate between using his falcata\
